================================================================================
Third-party data attribution
================================================================================

The demo storefront ("Nimbus") ships a committed, signed product catalog bundle
at `backend/examples/catalog/` (~728 products / ~6,356 reviews, clothing &
accessories). That catalog is derived from:

    Amazon E-commerce Products & Reviews Dataset
    Author:  lazylad99
    Source:  https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/lazylad99/amazon-e-commerce-product-and-review-dataset
    License: MIT
    Scope:   ~728 products / ~6,356 reviews, clothing & accessories,
             scraped from Amazon.com circa March 2025.

The committed bundle was produced from that dataset's raw CSVs via
`edgereco build-catalog` -> `edgereco index` -> `edgereco bundle`. You can
regenerate it from the raw CSVs with the same commands (see README).

